&chapter=34&verse=31'>Gen 34:31</a> <br/> - Achan hides the wedge of gold and the Babylonish garment<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=7&verse=26'>Jos 7:26</a> <br/> - Micah steals eleven hundred pieces of silver<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=17&verse=2'>Jdg 17:2</a> <br/> - Micah's priest steals his images<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=18&verse=21'>Jdg 18:21</a> <br/> - Joab's guile in securing Absalom's return<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=14&verse=20'>2Sa 14:20</a> <br/> - Ahab usurps Naboth's vineyard<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=21&verse=16'>1Ki 21:16</a> <br/> - Judas' hypocritical sympathy for the poor<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=12&verse=6'>Joh 12:6</a><br/><a href='S:Diplomacy'>Diplomacy</a>; <a href='S:Hypocrisy'>Hypocrisy</a>; <a href='S:Injustice'>Injustice</a>; <a href='S:Treason'>Treason</a> "}]}